Description: Support for automated analyses of ecological time series.  The goal is to support the ability of end users to run analyses on a collection of datasets. Users will be able to add datasets and/or analysis methods using code (in the case of data, code to bring the data into standardized formats), with functionality for Drake to automatically update downstream analyses and reports.
